            <li>GPU metrics reported by the Software will be accurate, complete, or timely;</li>
            <li>Memory leak detection or OOM predictions will correctly identify all issues or prevent out-of-memory conditions;</li>
            <li>The Software will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of harmful components;</li>
            <li>The Software will be compatible with all hardware configurations, operating systems, or GPU drivers.</li>
          </ul>
